history.content:
Come weave some webs with us at Web Development at Berkeley.
Web Development at Berkeley is Berkeley's first web development organization, bringing full-stack web dev education and industry development opportunities to our campus community and beyond.
We are an inclusive and motivated community of individuals who seek to learn, build, and innovate together. WDB strives to provide a safe place for people of all skill levels to get involved in the world of web dev.
We are thrilled to announce our Spring 2021 recruitment timeline. We have spots open for students and developers/designers, and we are so excited to meet you all.

Check us out on our socials to learn more about our mission and past projects
https://linktr.ee/webdevatberkeley

Come to our events to get to know us better
Infosession 1: https://fb.me/e/3AwN8GLp7
Infosession 2: https://fb.me/e/h7AWuyACZ
Meet & Greet: https://fb.me/e/12dA8OSzp

Sold? Send in your application today
https://webatberkeley.org/apply
